+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Post-Course Learning Pathway Guide**                                |
|                                                                       |
| Three tracks · Week 1 actions · 30-day milestones · 90-day goals      |
|                                                                       |
| *Module 12 \| BBC Academy / JBI Training \| Secure Web Application    |
| Development*                                                          |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Which track is right for you?** If you completed most practicals and
  felt stretched --- start with Explorer. If you completed all practicals
  including extension challenges and wanted more time --- start with
  Practitioner. If you completed Expert track challenges and found them
  straightforward --- Expert. You can move between tracks at any time.

