**Signposted Resources**

  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Resource**        **URL**                                            **Why it matters for this
                                                                         course**
  ------------------- -------------------------------------------------- ---------------------------------
  **PortSwigger Web   portswigger.net/web-security                       Free, lab-based, structured. The
  Security Academy**                                                     best single resource for all
                                                                         three tracks.

  **OWASP Juice Shop  pwning.owasp-juice.shop                            Official solutions and
  Companion Guide**                                                      walkthroughs for all Juice Shop
                                                                         challenges.

  **OWASP Cheat Sheet cheatsheetseries.owasp.org                         Definitive developer reference
  Series**                                                               for every OWASP category.
                                                                         Bookmark the Authentication, SQL
                                                                         Injection, and XSS cheat sheets
                                                                         first.

  **TryHackMe**       tryhackme.com                                      Guided rooms for hands-on
                                                                         offensive practice. Start with
                                                                         \"Jr Penetration Tester\"
                                                                         learning path.

  **CISA Known        cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog   Authoritative list of
  Exploited                                                              vulnerabilities actively
  Vulnerabilities**                                                      exploited in the wild. Mandatory
                                                                         patching reference for A06.

  **NVD --- National  nvd.nist.gov                                       Authoritative CVE details
  Vulnerability                                                          including CVSS vector strings.
  Database**                                                             Use for A06 CVE triage (Module 10
                                                                         card).
